        <p>
          Een website die niet alleen mooi is, maar ook klanten oplevert. 
          Snel, vindbaar in Google, en makkelijk zelf te beheren.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Responsive design (werkt op alle apparaten)
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Geoptimaliseerd voor zoekmachines (SEO)
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Contact- en offerteformulieren
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Snelle laadtijd (goed voor Google)
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
          Website laten maken
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Automatisering</h3>
        <p>
          Laat computers het saaie werk doen. Automatiseer repetitieve taken 
          en bespaar uren per week.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Automatische facturen & herinneringen
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Koppeling tussen je tools
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Automatische rapportages
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            E-mail workflows
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Meer weten
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Web Apps & Portalen</h3>
        <p>
          Maatwerk oplossingen voor specifieke bedrijfsprocessen. 
          Van klantportalen tot interne tools.
        </p>
        <ul class="service-features">
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Klantportalen & dashboards
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Boekingssystemen
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            Interne bedrijfstools
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            API koppelingen
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Meer weten
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background: var(--color-canvas);
    position: relative;
  }

  .services-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .services-intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    max-width: 55ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border: 1px solid rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.05);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .service-card-featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .service-card-featured {
      grid-row: span 2;
    }
  }

  .service-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .service-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 74, 0.1) 0%, rgba(255, 107, 74, 0.05) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .service-icon svg {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .service-card > p {
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .service-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .service-features li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-light);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.05);
  }

  .service-features li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .service-features svg {
    color: var(--color-success);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .service-card .btn {
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: auto;
  }
</style>
